message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $150. I think it's a great deal for something of this quality.
I'm really interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $90. Can you meet me at that price?
Thanks for the offer, Bob.  I understand your position, but $90 is just too low for me.  Could you do $130?
I'm still really interested in the product, but $130 is still a bit out of my budget. Can you meet me at $110?
